    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, representing the pinnacle of its model year. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, still retaining that new-car feel with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standards, ensuring it drives as perfectly as it looks. This is a rare find for a collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
