    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary choice for the driver who prioritizes both reliability and sophisticated engineering. This automobile has been maintained to a high standard, showcasing a well-preserved interior and a robust mechanical profile that ensures a confident driving experience. Offering a harmonious blend of performance and value, this unit stands as a testament to diligent ownership and remains in prime condition for its next proprietor. Contact our executive sales team to arrange a private viewing.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my trips around town. It\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and is just waiting for someone new to take it on its next adventure. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic car that\u2019s ready to hit the road right away. Come take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example benefits from proactive maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure optimal variable valve timing across the rev range. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the M-Variable differential lock provides predictable torque distribution during high-lateral-G maneuvers. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, it shows minor patina consistent with its enthusiast-driven history but remains mechanically robust and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior and title. Ready for road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a thorough walk-around will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the upholstery is clean and free of odors or punctures, with only light creasing on the driver's seat bolster to note. All onboard technology, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the car has been treated to regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake service, ensuring a smooth and reliable driving experience. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the undercarriage is clean with no signs of leaks. Included with the sale are two sets of keys and a complete folder of service receipts, proving this car has been loved and looked after.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of distinguished mechanical integrity and refined aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to ensure a driving experience characterized by stability, precision, and consistent performance. The interior remains remarkably well-preserved, reflecting a history of conscientious ownership and diligent care. For the discerning buyer seeking a sophisticated balance of proven reliability and exceptional value, this offering represents a premier opportunity in its class.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it to get you where you need to go without any fuss. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of life on the road, but honestly, it still looks great and runs even better! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, comfy car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated M96 flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus. This rear-wheel-drive example is mated to a G96 6-speed manual transaxle, providing short-throw precision and a direct mechanical connection. The chassis retains its factory-specified rigidity, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup for optimal kinematic control. Recent service includes a documented IMS bearing upgrade and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. While the finish shows light road patina, the drivetrain remains tight with linear power delivery across the rev range. This is a driver-focused specimen ideal for those prioritizing performance engineering over concours aesthetics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
